        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://poi-kb.org/ards/ventilation-strategy"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115 xml:lang="en">Lung-protective ventilation strategy using tidal volume 6 ml/kg predicted body weight with plateau pressure ≤30 cmH₂O. ARMA trial (PMID 10793162): mortality 31.0% vs 39.8% with 12 ml/kg (P=0.007). Prevents volutrauma; reduces systemic biotrauma. Universal standard of care for ARDS.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:hasDbXref>MESH:D012128</obo:hasDbXref>
        <obo:hasDbXref>UMLS:C0035222</obo:hasDbXref>
